highlights.text: “blue” by yung kai has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 213 days straight.
“Between Us (เพลงประกอบซีรีส์ Us รักของเรา)” by Bonnie Pattraphus is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #72.
LBI利比 has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “Jumping Machine (跳楼机)” is the highest at #7.
“Chest Pain (I Love)” by Malcolm Todd is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 17 spots at #38.
